@ attack element types
Physical - Swords, Axes
Ranged - Bows, Crossbows

Fire - Strong against Ice
Ice - Strong against Wind
Wind - Strong against Fire

Earth - Strong against Lightning
Lightning - Strong against Water
Water - Strong against Earth

Holy - unblockable, usually has positive effects
Sin - unblockable, usually has a really powerful effect but at a cost
Mortal - ignores all buffs & debuffs, always crits, ignores type advantages

@ attack attack type
Slash - balanced moderate
Pierce - high single target
Blunt - low multi target
Crush - high slow 
Magic - elemental
Support - buffs & debuffs
Status - inflicts status effects
